    Task

    Explore Platform Offerings

    As a potential customer looking for quality control solutions, I explore the product offerings available on the website, so that I can better understand how the platform meets my quality management needs.

    Success definition: Given I am on the Factored Quality homepage When I click on the Product button, then I see a dropdown with options for Platform, Services, and API Then I should be able to navigate to the Platform page where I can view features and services related to quality control.
